1. *Cevi* su instalirane duž cele zgrade. (Pipes are installed throughout the building.)
2. Molim vas da zamenite *cev* u kuhinji, procurila je. (Please replace the *pipe* in the kitchen, it's leaking.)
3. Oni su proizvođači različitih vrsta *cevi*. (They are manufacturers of different types of *tubes*.)
4. Radnik je spojio dve *cevi* koristeći lepak. (The worker joined two *pipes* using glue.)
5. *Cevi* u kupatilu treba redovno održavati kako bi se sprečile blokade. (The *pipes* in the bathroom need to be regularly maintained to prevent blockages.)
6. Rekli su mi da *cev* za ventilaciju ne radi ispravno. (They told me that the *duct* for ventilation is not working properly.)
7. Molim vas da smanjite buku koju prave te metalne *cevi*. (Please reduce the noise that those metal *tubes* are making.)
8. Kupili smo nekoliko metara bakarnih *cevi* za našu vodovodnu instalaciju. (We bought several meters of copper *pipes* for our plumbing installation.)
9. Ukoliko primetite bilo kakvu oštećenost na *cevima*, odmah nas obavestite. (If you notice any damage to the *pipes*, please let us know immediately.)
10. Voda iz ovih *cevi* je veoma hladna, naročito u zimskim mesecima. (Water from these *pipes* is very cold, especially in winter months.)